OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with sunny spells northeast
OL,6,Fat first then cloud and rain in the
OL,7,Fsouthwest soon spreads northeast
OL,8,Fbecoming heavy at times. This rain
OL,9,Fwill clear to sunny spells and
OL,10,Fscattered showers in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright or clear spells with
OL,13,Fthe occasional shower at first
OL,14,Fbecoming cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain, some heavy, towards the morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy rain becoming drier
OL,19,Fwith bright spells towards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
